Subject: drm/i915/hdcp: Clean up local variables
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 486bba4524e00c23a8cca2159ae537234d8178ac
